			<div class="wiki-info">
				The Mimic will mimic one ghost at a time, copying all features and abilities of that ghost.
				It changes ghost type every 30 seconds to 2 minutes, but cannot change during hunts.
				<br />The Mimic can mimic a mimic or player. It will be a blank ghost without any special abilities.
				<br /><br />
				The Mimic provides evidence of Ghost Orbs as additional piece of evidence.
				These Ghost Orbs are fake and an ability of The Mimic. They will always appear, regardless of the amount of evidences obtainable.
			</div>
